1. *Devojkama* se sviđaju pokloni. (Girls like presents.)
2. Pošao sam u grad sa *devojkama*. (I went to the city with the girls.)
3. *Devojkama* sam rekao da će biti zabava. (I told the girls there will be fun.)
4. Zabrinut sam za *devojke*. (I'm worried about the girls.)
5. Sve *devojke* su bile oduševljene poklonima. (All the girls were thrilled with the presents.)
6. *Devojke* su bile srećne jer su dobile nove haljine. (The girls were happy because they got new dresses.)
7. Često idem u šetnju sa *devojkama*. (I often go for a walk with the girls.)
8. *Devojkama* je bilo dosadno na žurki. (The girls were bored at the party.)
9. Zamolio sam *devojke* da mi pomognu oko pripreme večere. (I asked the girls to help me with dinner preparation.)
10. *Devojkama* se sviđaju različite vrste cveća. (Girls like different types of flowers.)